Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lords are all corrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They do nothing but battle day and night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They refuse to listen to the teachings of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As such, the pretender to the throne,\NTheo Cornaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is now monopolizing the Crests,\Nshards of the One God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and is attempting to claim\Nthe Continent as his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As God's representative,\NI hereby declare the start of a holy war!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the Order of the Crest\Nwould become our enemy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Order of the Crest thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they trying to thwart us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must mean that the Order of the Crest\Nand the Mage Academy are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was last night that the Mage Academy\Npurged the Lord-supporting Mages,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and chose the path of war against the Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The very next day, the Order of the Crest\Ndeclared holy war on the Imperial Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but they've positioned\Nthemselves to block the path to Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't just be a coincidence, now, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How big is the Papal Force, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have 2,000 holy warriors,\Nand around 3,000 mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they have over 70,000 followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, that includes a great number\Nof women, children, and the elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holy warriors and mercenaries are one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I have no desire to fight innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you've always fought\Nfor the sake of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't fight, then I'll fight for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will not come to a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because that is not the wish of the One God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go see Sir Leone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall convince him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You would do that for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Pope is calling you a fake,\Nclaiming that he himself is the Holy Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you went to see a man like that,\Nyou could be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because that is the duty I must fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should try her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Pope has his followers taking\Nto the battlefield, you cannot fight the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, we can't sit here with our hands tied,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or the Papal Army would eventually attack,\Nshielding itself with those followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should that comes to pass,\Nthere's a chance our forces may be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it would be a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's still no reason for me\Nto send her into danger alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to accompany her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what is the Imperial Army up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've positioned themselves on a hill,\Nand have shown no sign of making a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They must be stricken with fear\Nof the One God and the Pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That youngling, Theo Cornaro, will soon prostrate\Nhimself before you, and beg for your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about my followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that they've gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, they also seem hesitant\Nabout fighting the hero, Theo Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their morale is not high by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they know that the Holy Maiden Priscilla\Nserves the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those in the Holy Maiden faction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,have been preaching that Theo Cornaro will offer\Nthe Grancrest to the Holy Maiden Priscilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the One God will then be revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have greater numbers, but in terms of skill\Nand equipment, the Imperial Army is superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it will be difficult to defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to win this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it might be better to be royally defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If rumors spread that the Lords\Nmassacred followers of the Order,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo Cornaro's reputation will surely suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Gunther, start preparing for your attack\Non the Imperial Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning, launch an attack\Nwith the followers in the vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the holy warriors\Nand the mercenaries in camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo, I didn't expect you\Nto see me off personally. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll persuade the Pope no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's our intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that broom for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The leader of the White Witches\Nshowed me how to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's not as easy to use as a wand,\Nbut having it enables me to focus better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irvin. Aishela.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Please, look after these two.\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I owe her for saving my life twice.\NTime to pay her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, we'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put our faith in those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Grace, we have come today\Nto ask a favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I may, Your Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor Theo does not wish\Nto engage you in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Imperial Army's objective\Nis to quell the disturbance in Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is fine with me.\NHowever, I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He is to hand over all of the Crests\Nin the Imperial Army's possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crests are for reviving the One God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any who monopolizes those Crests\Nmust be punished no matter who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for even the emperor himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Emperor Theo\Nis not monopolizing the Crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The emperor's goal is to use the Grancrest\Nto eradicate the Chaos across the Continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that the same goal for the Order?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That by the power of the One God,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos shall be eradicated from the Continent\Nto create a paradise for this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Imperial Army and the Order\Nhave the same goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- She's lying to escape God's wrath.\N- Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! I won't allow you to mislead\Nour followers with such lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are not lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Leone. It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Did he say that's Lady Priscilla?\N- The one foretold to be the Holy Grail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor Theo is always professing his intent to end\Nthe age of Chaos, as long as it's in his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that means reviving the One God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the job of His Eminence,\Nthe Pope, as God's representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something a brat of humble birth\Nshould be allowed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does one's social standing have to do\Nwith the noble act of reviving God?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should all be equal before God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Joseph, we're about to go into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we set up another opportunity\Nfor Priestess Priscilla to explain herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because Sir Theo has no intention of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Sir Theo\Nis not a follower of the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But my father, Ernest, founder of our Order,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,told us repeatedly that we mustn't force\Nour faith on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've all heard that before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NThat's what the Founder used to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- She's right!\N- That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'd like you to recall\Nthe Founder's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the One God is revived,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we will be saved from our suffering\Nunder the Chaos, and the grief of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day will arrive when we find ourselves\Nin paradise, rather than a paradise after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:11:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the radiance of the Holy Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Holy Grail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo will be the one\Nto bring an end to the age of Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I received the revelation\Nto go to Sir Theo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was so that I could witness his noble deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Maiden Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, that girl\Nwill be anointed leader of the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once its master's strength depletes,\Na Crest transforms into a Chaos Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show our followers the sight of the Holy Grail\Nturning into a Chaos Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come to fulfill the mission of those\Nwho've sworn fealty to Pandora's principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to have been a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Emperor Theo has claimed the Crests as his own,\Nand Priestess Priscilla is supporting that."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was taken in by Priest Joseph's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Leone, offer you my heartfelt apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also accept the Imperial Army's offer of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, receive the Grancrest from Emperor Theo\None day, and revive the One God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that should be my duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Capture those heretics!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As Pope, I have declared\NPriestess Priscilla to be a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Upon asking the One God to judge her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I received the revelation\Nthat I must inflict death on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget why we came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill the Pope now,\Nwar will become unavoidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, everything that Priscilla just did\Nwill have been for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This Holy Grail is a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As such, it will soon shatter,\Nand turn into a Chaos Core!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course it will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Crests shatter and turn into Chaos Cores\Nwhen their owners die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the duty that I must fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As Priestess Priscilla's co-conspirators,\Nyou are all destined to suffer eternally in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're saying\Nthat it was a sin to ally with Priscilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll gladly go to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But don't think you can take our lives so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Followers of the Order of the Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And how did it make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla always said\Nthat you could find faith in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Maiden Priscilla\Nwas the true Holy Grail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who destroyed it\Nwas the fake Holy Grail, the Pope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holy warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Behead them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This wasn't supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla's Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not turning into a Chaos Core?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real Holy Grail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Priscilla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't it turn into a Chaos Core?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she must have been a true Holy Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You said that she wasn't a real Holy Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you just need to seize her Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you can become the true Holy Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's a grave enough sin\Nto have killed a Holy Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do such a dreadful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to betray Pandora?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than falling to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have no more use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow you to kill a crucial suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to pursue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we killed him, nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to summon Sir Theo instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... What have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is as you just witnessed\Nwith your own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As Priscilla has proclaimed,\Nthe emperor will surely revive the One God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was the duty that she had to fulfill?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca has requested that you come\Nto the Order's camp as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, I will protect you\Neven at the cost of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind not saying things like\N"at the cost of my life"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone else to die before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t go down that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We may have avoided a battle\Nwith the Papal Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but a battle against\Nthe Mage Academy awaits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many lives will be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you are the one who must not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared myself for this, but to be honest,\Nmy heart's about to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm the one who killed Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sent her to see the Pope,\Nknowing how dangerous it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one but that girl could have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And some things can only be done by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla. I'm going to inherit your Holy Grail now,\Nalong with your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I vow to bring an end to the age of Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the duty that I must fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will now assume custodianship\Nof your Holy Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Please bring an end\Nto the age of Chaos, Sir Theo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And create a world\Nwhere people can live in peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Emperor Theo Cornaro has become\Nthe guardian of the Holy Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who believe in the One God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let us worship the emperor,\Nand become his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's terrified\Nbecause he murdered a true Holy Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We captured him to investigate the link between\Nthe Mage Academy and the Order of the Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll let you deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, the sight of him fills me with rage\Nthat I might do something to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THE HOLY GRAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 23\NCASTLE WALLS
